    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Fluorescent spot test for glucose-6-phosphate dehydrogenase (G6PD) deficiency was performed in 5 boys and 14 girls who had confirmed COVID-19. Out of those, 4 (80%) boys and 5 (36%) girls were found to be G6PD deficient.</jats:p>",
